---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Cerere trimisă · Hectar"
  description="Cererea ta a fost primită. Îți răspundem în aceeași zi."
  canonical="/contact/trimis"
  noindex={true}
>
  <div class="success-page">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="success-card">
        <div class="success-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="72" height="72" viewBox="0 0 72 72" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <circle cx="36" cy="36" r="36" fill="#4A5D3A" opacity="0.08"/>
            <circle cx="36" cy="36" r="26" fill="#4A5D3A" opacity="0.12"/>
            <circle cx="36" cy="36" r="18" fill="#4A5D3A"/>
            <path d="M26 36l7 7 13-13" stroke="#F7F3EA" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>

        <h1>Mulțumim! Cererea a ajuns la noi.</h1>
        <p class="lead">Îți răspundem în aceeași zi, de obicei în câteva ore. Verifică inbox-ul (și folderul de spam, uneori ne strecoară acolo).</p>

        <div class="next-steps">
          <h2>Ce urmează</h2>
          <div class="steps">
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-num" aria-hidden="true">1</div>
              <div>
                <strong>Analizăm cererea ta</strong>
                <p>Verificăm disponibilitatea în zona ta și estimăm costul exact.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-num" aria-hidden="true">2</div>
              <div>
                <strong>Îți trimitem oferta</strong>
                <p>Preț clar, fără costuri ascunse. Confirmi sau nu — fără presiune.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-num" aria-hidden="true">3</div>
              <div>
                <strong>Venim la câmp</strong>
                <p>Tratamentul se face, primești raportul GPS. Plătești după.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="urgent-note">
          <p>Dacă e urgent sau vrei să vorbești direct:</p>
          <a href="tel:+40700000000" class="phone-link">0700 000 000</a>
          <span class="phone-note">Lun–Sâm · 07:00–21:00</span>
        </div>

        <div class="success-actions">
          <a href="/" class="btn-primary">Înapoi acasă</a>
          <a href="/servicii" class="btn-secondary">Explorează serviciile</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .success-page {
    min-height: 70vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding-block: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .success-card {
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    text-align: center;
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: var(--space-2xl);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }

  .success-icon {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .success-card h1 {
    font-size: var(--fs-h2);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    line-height: var(--lh-heading);
  }

  .lead {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: var(--fs-body);
    line-height: var(--lh-relaxed);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    max-width: 400px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  /* Steps */
  .next-steps {
    background: var(--color-bg-deep);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    text-align: left;
  }

  .next-steps h2 {
    font-size: var(--fs-body);
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    text-align: center;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .steps {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .step {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .step-num {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: #fff;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: var(--fs-xs);
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
  }

  .step strong { font-size: var(--fs-small); display: block; margin-bottom: 2px; }
  .step p { font-size: var(--fs-xs); color: var(--color-text-muted); margin: 0; line-height: var(--lh-relaxed); }

  /* Urgent */
  .urgent-note {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }
  .urgent-note p { font-size: var(--fs-small); color: var(--color-text-muted); margin: 0; }

  .phone-link {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-tight);
    transition: color var(--duration-fast) var(--ease);
  }
  .phone-link:hover { color: var(--color-primary-dark); }

  .phone-note { font-size: var(--fs-xs); color: var(--color-text-muted); }

  /* Actions */
  .success-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
</style>
